title: Aattanayagann
subTitle: Lingam is shocked after his sister-in-law informs him that his brother, Chandran, is a dreaded gangster. To set things right, Lingam decides to reform his brother.

title: Kumbakkarai Thangaiah
subTitle: Mangamma, who is in love with Thangaiya, is distraught while he faces a tough predicament owing to a disagreement in their village.

title: Engeyo Ketta Kural
subTitle: Ponni wants to live a lavish life but gets married to her cousin Kumaran. Her love for worldly pleasures makes her abandon Kumaran and her daughter for a richer man.

title: Ponnana Neram
subTitle: A young college girl, who enjoys playing pranks on others, gets into trouble with a group of terrorists. A brave police officer comes to her rescue and sets on a mission to wipe out the gang.

title: Dharma
subTitle: Intolerant of injustice, Dharma is arrested for killing a man for molesting his sister. Upon his release, he becomes a powerful gangster to fight off evil in society.

title: Azhagarsamy
subTitle: Thayama gets money from a landlord in order to save her husband and promises to give her child in return. Things turn for the worst when the rich man wants to marry off his daughter to Thayama's son.
During a curfew imposed in two quarreling villages, a small-time thief, a driver and an artist team up to steal gold from an unjust politician.

title: Otran
subTitle: A group of terrorists kidnaps Sudha and takes over her apartment to save their employer Robert. Karthik, a RAW agent, pretends to be a cook and goes to her house to capture the entire gang.
